  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "The Wild is an single-player, side-scrolling adventure game starring zoo animals trying to get back to the wild. Players to take on the role of Samson and Benny through 18 levels of action, as they journey from the New York City zoo to the wilds in search of Ryan, Samson's lost teenage son. Lava-spewing volcanoes, falling stalactites, angry dogs, charging wildebeests and other obstacles are waiting for you to overcome them!",
